#

Hummus and Veggie Toast

10 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganHigh Fiber

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

QuickHealthySnack

Description

A quick, nutritious toast topped with creamy hummus and colorful veggies, perfect for a light meal or snack.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • hummus: 1/2 cup
  • cucumber, sliced: 1/2
  • tomato, sliced: 1
  • radishes, thinly sliced: 4
  • avocado, sliced: 1/2
  • fresh parsley, chopped: 2 tablespoons
